overview: Rory Knox used to go once a month but that changed because Cody and her we getting more than real close.  Mr. Mancini was a new client for Britt Blair and he was very handsome. She was immediately attracted to him, unfortunately, he was also her best friend's Dad.  Kay Lovely's client Derrick was very handsome and athletic. He comes to her for a deep tissue message. Kay's fantasy's come true, she gives him more than just a message.  Johnny is a great masseuse and has excellent techniques. He came recommended by one of Kira Perez best friends and he happened to be really cute.
title: Massage Parlor 3
